campus for my very first tour I just knew

00:00:28.330 --> 00:00:29.430
that I could live here.

00:00:29.430 --> 00:00:33.970
(0:30) I fell in love with the campus that
day, I applied as soon as I got the opportunity.

00:00:33.970 --> 00:00:37.260
(0:34) My tour guide completely sold me, the
whole process.

00:00:37.260 --> 00:00:41.420
There's always cultural events going on, there
is always music al events, there is sporting

00:00:41.420 --> 00:00:44.710
events, there's clubs, organizations groups
volunteering.

00:00:44.710 --> 00:00:47.720
The world's largest water balloon fight and
here's ten percent off at the book and store

00:00:47.720 --> 00:00:49.430
and I was like I'm sold.

00:00:49.430 --> 00:00:51.000
Like this place can't get much better.

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:55.100
(0:51) A lot of kids when they come to a campus
and they are just like I would never be able

00:00:55.100 --> 00:00:57.559
to find my way around but I have never had
that feeling.

00:00:57.559 --> 00:01:01.449
(0:57) You've got people that are so welcome
and so warm they are always looking to help

00:01:01.449 --> 00:01:02.449
you.

00:01:02.449 --> 00:01:03.449
(1:01) I just want to be here.

00:01:03.449 --> 00:01:05.199
There is not a day that I don't want to be
on campus.

00:01:05.199 --> 00:01:07.110
(1:04) The campus is absolutely beautiful.

00:01:07.110 --> 00:01:10.619
There are a lot of flowers and pretty spots
and pretty benches.

00:01:10.619 --> 00:01:14.650
(1:11) As soon as you step foot on campus
I felt a part of the family.

00:01:14.650 --> 00:01:16.140
(1:14) Campus is very safe.

00:01:16.140 --> 00:01:20.870
There are these paths with huge paw prints
and it's called the Cat's Path and these are

00:01:20.870 --> 00:01:22.090
very well lit areas.

00:01:22.090 --> 00:01:25.310
I really appreciate living on such a safe
campus.

00:01:25.310 --> 00:01:27.909
(1:25) I am a sucker for Commons.

00:01:27.909 --> 00:01:32.170
Not only because it's five feet from my dorm
but it can't get better than a buffet.

00:01:32.170 --> 00:01:34.010
(1:31) I really like Ovid's.

00:01:34.010 --> 00:01:35.960
