00:01:46.840 --> 00:01:49.620
(1:46) You learn more about different cultures
and to just hangout with different people

00:01:49.620 --> 00:01:50.799
from all around the world.

00:01:50.799 --> 00:01:54.260
(1:50) Just getting to meet new people from
