00:03:11.880 --> 00:03:16.060
(3:12) You're not just a number here at UK.
(3:15) He just had a way of making the class

00:03:16.060 --> 00:03:17.790
fun and making you want to learn.

00:03:17.790 --> 00:03:22.070
(3:18) They really want you to succeed they
are there to help you and guide you.

00:03:22.070 --> 00:03:23.540
(3:21) My advisor is awesome.

00:03:23.540 --> 00:03:26.270
(3:24) They are emailing you internship opportunities.

00:03:26.270 --> 00:03:31.560
(3:27) I got to intern in the State Senate,
the British Parliament and the U.S. Congress.

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:35.040
(3:32) You really get to discover who you
are and what you're capable of.

00:03:35.040 --> 00:03:39.500
Like this internship where you look around
and you've got people from Harvard, Yale and

00:03:39.500 --> 00:03:43.540
not only am I competing with them in terms
of our projects or assignments I'm exceling

00:03:43.540 --> 00:03:44.540
past them.

00:03:44.540 --> 00:03:46.800
(3:45) UK core is essential.

00:03:46.800 --> 00:03:52.220
It allows students to take classes that are
going to benefit them in where they want to

00:03:52.220 --> 00:03:53.220
go.

00:03:53.220 --> 00:03:55.040
(3:53) UK is really becoming an elite school.

00:03:55.040 --> 00:04:00.140
(3:35) We are going to have the most modern
living learning space you can find anywhere

00:04:00.140 --> 00:04:01.480
in the country.

00:04:01.480 --> 00:04:04.860
Where relationships will be born, where innovations
will be born.

00:04:04.860 --> 00:04:09.070
(4:05) With this Kentucky promise I think
a vision greater than any of us could imagine.

00:04:09.070 --> 00:04:14.000
(4:09) The amount of things that are possible
on this campus is just amazing.

00:04:14.000 --> 00:04:16.979
(4:15) It's really important to get involved.

00:04:16.979 --> 00:04:20.910
(4:17) K Week is the best way to get involved
from the beginning.

00:04:20.910 --> 00:04:24.979
K Week was just a great overall icebreaker
to the whole college experience.

00:04:24.979 --> 00:04:31.680
It's nine days of nonstop fun, free food,
free t-shirts, tons of people everywhere.

00:04:31.680 --> 00:04:35.509
If you pay for a meal during K Week you have
done something wrong.

00:04:35.509 --> 00:04:40.580
(4:35) Just the opportunities that are made
available it makes you want to try new things.

00:04:40.580 --> 00:04:44.430
(4:41) If you look at some of the organizations
that have grown over the past couple years.

